26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_devinit_g98.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "nv50.h"
30
31#include <subdev/bios.h>
32#include <subdev/bios/init.h>
33
34static u64
35g98_devinit_disable(struct nvkm_devinit *init)
36{
37 struct nvkm_device *device = init->subdev.device;
38 u32 r001540 = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x001540);
39 u32 r00154c = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x00154c);
40 u64 disable = 0ULL;
41
42 if (!(r001540 & 0x40000000)) {
43 disable |= (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_MSPDEC);
44 disable |= (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_MSVLD);
45 disable |= (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_MSPPP);
46 }
47
48 if (!(r00154c & 0x00000004))
49 disable |= (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_DISP);
50 if (!(r00154c & 0x00000020))
51 disable |= (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_MSVLD);
52 if (!(r00154c & 0x00000040))
53 disable |= (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_SEC);
54
55 return disable;
56}
57
58static const struct nvkm_devinit_func
59g98_devinit = {
60 .preinit = nv50_devinit_preinit,
61 .init = nv50_devinit_init,
62 .post = nv04_devinit_post,
63 .pll_set = nv50_devinit_pll_set,
64 .disable = g98_devinit_disable,
65};
66
67int
68g98_devinit_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index,
69 struct nvkm_devinit **pinit)
70{
71 return nv50_devinit_new_(&g98_devinit, device, index, pinit);
72}
